└─ SuperCo
   ├─ AuthOnboardingStack
   │   ├─ Login
   │   ├─ Signup (with invite/org email)
   │   └─ RoleRedirect (Supervisor Only)
   └─ Tabs (Bottom Navigation)
       ├─ Home
       │   ├─ TodayView
       │   │   ├─ Shows real-time team status: Present, Late, WFH, On Leave
       │   │   └─ Color-coded by team (Web, Mobile, AI)
       │   ├─ QuickActions
       │   │   ├─ One-tap approve/reject for leave/overtime
       │   │   └─ Reassign shift/task quickly
       │   ├─ CalendarSummary
       │   │   ├─ Heatmap of leave/shift coverage
       │   │   └─ Flags potential understaffing or overload
       │
       ├─ Team
       │   ├─ TeamList
       │   │   ├─ Filter by department
       │   │   └─ Status icons (Leave, Remote, Present)
       │   ├─ MemberProfile
       │   │   ├─ Skills, tags, attendance %, leave balance
       │   │   └─ Personal notes / 1:1 tracker
       │   ├─ ScheduleAssign
       │   │   ├─ Drag-drop shift planner
       │   │   └─ Schedule conflict detection
       │
       ├─ Approval
       │   ├─ LeaveApprovals
       │   │   ├─ Clash alerts (same-day leave)
       │   │   └─ Attendance & workload context
       │   ├─ OvertimeApprovals
       │   │   ├─ Reason + project link
       │   │   └─ Optional approval comment
       │   ├─ RequestHistory
       │   │   ├─ Filter by team or date
       │   │   └─ See who approved what
       │
       └─ Settings
           ├─ Announcements
           │   ├─ Push notices to teams
           │   └─ Rich formatting (links, urgency tag)
           ├─ Notifications
           │   └─ All alerts (approvals, reminders)
           ├─ Settings
           │   └─ Theme, profile, notification prefs
           └─ Feedback
               ├─ Report bugs / request features
               └─ View changelog & updates
